    <a title="Susan&#39;s Reviews" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19736308-susan-s-reviews"><img alt="Susan&#39;s Reviews" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1507651790p2/19736308.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2891955977?book_show_action=true">Jul 11, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Susan&#39;s Reviews" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Susan&#39;s Reviews" href="/user/show/19736308-susan-s-reviews">Susan&#39;s Reviews</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2891955977" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12120832005743900316">I thought Jennifer was &quot;the bomb&quot; as the kids like to say. She inspired me, and I almost wanted to become a criminal lawyer like Jennifer, but I realized that only Perry Mason&apos;s clients were ever always innocent, so I decided to take a different life path! Another great Sidney Sheldon read from my misspent youth!</span>
  <span id="freeText12120832005743900316" style="display:none">I thought Jennifer was "the bomb" as the kids like to say. She inspired me, and I almost wanted to become a criminal lawyer like Jennifer, but I realized that only Perry Mason's clients were ever always innocent, so I decided to take a different life path! Another great Sidney Sheldon read from my misspent youth!</span>
