<span id="freeTextContainer416503541275382080">My First Sidney Sheldon and I fell in love.<br/><br/>The story never gave a hint that it would be such a heart breaking novel at the beginning at all.I had guessed that the trouble that had began for Jeniffer at the start of the story will be overcomed by her and she would have a beautiful happy ending.<br/>Boy was i in for a Shock.<br/>Conclusion : Never take for grated the happy ending for a story and be ready to have you own heart broken in pieces over it.<br/><br/><a class='jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction'>(view spoiler)</a><span class='spoilerContainer' style='display: none'>[<br/>I loved Jeniffer&apos;s character ,she had a ne</span></span>
