        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer12873209" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9699247153129121951">Crime, justice, sex, romance, family, love...<br/>All you want when you read a book is already in this book. Sheldon was always successful to describe anything so clear and easy to understand/imagine. <br/><br/>He described crime like it is not as sinful as it sounds, he described justice like it&apos;s not just about law, he described sex and make me agree that sex has so many shadows, he described romance and make people like me think that romance can be sweet too, and he described family just as it is.<br/><br/>And he des</span>
  <span id="freeText9699247153129121951" style="display:none">Crime, justice, sex, romance, family, love...<br />All you want when you read a book is already in this book. Sheldon was always successful to describe anything so clear and easy to understand/imagine. <br /><br />He described crime like it is not as sinful as it sounds, he described justice like it's not just about law, he described sex and make me agree that sex has so many shadows, he described romance and make people like me think that romance can be sweet too, and he described family just as it is.<br /><br />And he described love like...<br />Somehow, it's about someone who sacrifies everything without even thinking that what he/she is doing is a sacrifice...</span>
  <a data-text-id="9699247153129121951" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

